1) find a word
2) print out the corresponding number of letters as underscores, word => _  _  _  _
3) determine number of guesses

::: Gameplay loop :::

while: guessesLeft > 0

1) Guess a letter
2) Check how many times the letter occur
3) Print out the instancess of letter if present.
4) If letter not present, guessesLeft--
5) If all letters guessed, exit game.

-- Additionals --
1. Print letters and undercores
2. Print letters guessed
3. Print guessesLeft



